        "{t:'Lisa likes cats. She has three cats at home. They drink milk every morning.',qs:[{q:'How many cats does Lisa have?',a:['Three','Two'],c:0},{q:'What do the cats drink?',a:['Water','Milk'],c:1}]},"
        "{t:'It is raining today. Ben takes his umbrella. He walks to school slowly.',qs:[{q:'What is the weather like?',a:['Sunny','Rainy'],c:1},{q:'What does Ben take?',a:['His umbrella','His hat'],c:0}]},"
        "{t:'Sara can swim very fast. She goes to the pool on Saturdays. Her coach is Mrs. Green.',qs:[{q:'When does Sara go to the pool?',a:['On Saturdays','On Mondays'],c:0},{q:'Who is her coach?',a:['Mr. Brown','Mrs. Green'],c:1}]},"
        "{t:'The bird is in the tree. It sings a beautiful song. Two baby birds listen.',qs:[{q:'Where is the bird?',a:['In the tree','On the roof'],c:0},{q:'How many baby birds are there?',a:['Three','Two'],c:1}]}];"
